query:
INSERT INTO prioritization_criteria (name, description, category, weight, scoringGuideline, displayOrder) VALUES
('Urgency', 'How urgently does this project need to be addressed? Consider immediate safety risks, system failures, or regulatory deadlines.', 'risk', 20.00, '10=Critical/Immediate (within 1 year), 7-9=High (1-2 years), 4-6=Medium (2-4 years), 1-3=Low (4+ years)', 1),
('Mission Criticality', 'How critical is this facility to the organization''s core mission and operations?', 'strategic', 18.00, '10=Mission-critical facility, 7-9=High importance, 4-6=Moderate importance, 1-3=Low importance', 2),
('Safety', 'What is the safety risk to occupants, staff, or the public if this project is deferred?', 'risk', 17.00, '10=Life safety risk, 7-9=High injury risk, 4-6=Moderate risk, 1-3=Low/no safety risk', 3),
('Code Compliance', 'Does this project address code violations, accessibility requirements, or regulatory mandates?', 'compliance', 15.00, '10=Critical violations/legal mandate, 7-9=Significant non-compliance, 4-6=Minor issues, 1-3=Fully compliant', 4),
('Energy Savings', 'What is the potential for energy cost savings and environmental impact reduction?', 'financial', 12.00, '10=Very high savings (>30%), 7-9=High savings (20-30%), 4-6=Moderate savings (10-20%), 1-3=Low savings (<10%)', 5),
('Accessibility', 'Does this project improve accessibility for people with disabilities?', 'compliance', 8.00, '10=Critical ADA compliance, 7-9=Significant improvement, 4-6=Moderate improvement, 1-3=Minimal impact', 6),
('Environmental Impact', 'What is the environmental benefit (sustainability, green building, climate resilience)?', 'environmental', 5.00, '10=Major environmental benefit, 7-9=Significant benefit, 4-6=Moderate benefit, 1-3=Minimal benefit', 7),
('Operational Efficiency', 'Will this project improve operational efficiency, reduce maintenance costs, or extend asset life?', 'operational', 5.00, '10=Major efficiency gains, 7-9=Significant improvement, 4-6=Moderate improvement, 1-3=Minimal improvement', 8)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE name=name
